<h1>Welcome!</h1>
<p>Welcome to the BYU-Idaho American Sign Language Association home page! Most people think that in order to join "ASL Association you have to know ASL, but this is not true. We are happy to have anyone come learn how to communicate in ASL, and welcome all skill levels! We hope to help you develop strong friendships and an understanding of ASL and Deaf culture via fun activities and games. We teach everyday signs as well as gospel signs. Hope to see you there!</p>
